'''New Year's Day''' was a [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] [[holiday]]. On one occasion, eight years after they were taken down from public display, the [[Museum of Fine Art|Coronet City Museum of Fine Art]] gave a private showing of [[Venthan Chassu/Legends|Chassu's]] [[Selonian nude studies]] for four hours, 10,000 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] per person.

